episodes.synopsis: It's the start of the most exciting and dangerous time of year for the swampers: the monthlong alligator season.
episodes.title: Big Head Bites It

episodes.synopsis: Alligators are among the most territorial of animals, and they won't hesitate to eat smaller gators that wander into their feeding grounds.
episodes.title: Cannibal Gator

episodes.synopsis: As the swampers race toward the end of gator season, Tommy and Joe have a poacher after their catch and vow swamp justice.
episodes.title: Swamp Wars

episodes.synopsis: It's the final two days of alligator season. There are still a lot of gators to catch, not the least of which is the big daddy of all cannibal gators.
episodes.title: The Last Battle

episodes.synopsis: With more than 300 tags left, Troy and Jacob check out a new spot. Joe and Tommy are off to a strong start, but a mistake could cost them.
episodes.title: Hunter or Hunted?

episodes.synopsis: R.J. and Jay Paul are challenging Troy and Jacob, who struggle without their sharpshooter, Clint. Seasoned hunter Bruce sets out on his own.
episodes.title: Shooting Wild

episodes.synopsis: Troy's aiming to catch 25 gators with the help of his new partner, Liz. A poacher targets R.J., and Willie sets out on his own boat.
episodes.title: Hot Pursuit

episodes.synopsis: When Troy's sharpshooter, Liz, is injured, it threatens to slow him down. Bruce is used to hunting alone but decides to try his luck with a young local.
episodes.title: Dark Waters

episodes.synopsis: As the season kicks off with a major price increase, the hunters are eager to get started. Some teams reunite, while others venture off on their own.
episodes.title: Gator Gold Rush

episodes.synopsis: With his stepdad injured, Tommy hunts alone for the first time. Bruce's team heads to Stinky Bayou, while Liz and Kristi check out a dangerous spot.
episodes.title: Monster Marsh

episodes.synopsis: Troy discovers that his family is in danger. R.J. and Paul conduct an ancient tribal ceremony before taking on a formidable gator nicknamed "Bigfoot."
episodes.title: Avenged

episodes.synopsis: Two weeks into alligator season, the hunters struggle to catch up after losing time during the storm. Troy and Clint brave a dangerous swamp.
episodes.title: Gates of Hell

episodes.synopsis: In the second half of gator season, the younger hunters step up to the plate. A nighttime trip to the swamp puts Jay Paul and a friend in danger.
episodes.title: Young Blood

episodes.synopsis: The hunting teams must change partners. Jacob's new partner, Marie Lacoste, shares some innovative hunting methods.
episodes.title: Deadly Duo

episodes.synopsis: With only two days left in the season, the hunters rush to tag out, but cold weather threatens their progress.
episodes.title: Deadly Divide

video.title: Swamp People: Collection
video.synopsis: Follow groups of tough and resourceful Swampers as they hunt alligators during the 30-day season in the wild swamplands of Southern Louisiana.
